                    <span style="font-size: 0.4em; margin-top: 5px;" id="trend-score">Trend: --</span>
                </div>

                <div class="analysis-box">
                    <h3>üìä An√°lise em Tempo Real</h3>

                    <div class="analysis-section" id="patterns-section" style="display: none;">
